Our BIG ANNOUNCEMENT!
Thank you for the incredible support and trust you’ve shown Salt Oral Care.

When we started this journey nearly two years ago, we had no idea it would resonate so deeply and bring together such a passionate, loyal community. Your love, encouragement, and honest feedback have shaped who we are — and we take every bit of it to heart.

With Lotus Holdings backing us, here’s to growing our tribe of like-minded individuals and continuing to build something truly meaningful, together.

With gratitude,
Karan & Viraj
